## 4. Dataset

The input file `dataset.csv` contains **~25,920 rows** with 3 columns:

| Column | Example | Description |
|--------|---------|-------------|
| `Timestamp` | `2025-11-01 0:00:00` | 5-minute interval readings |
| `Server_ID` | `S1`, `S2`, `S3` | 3 servers being monitored |
| `Power_Usage_Watts` | `78`, `163`, `112` | Power draw in Watts |

- **Date range**: Nov 1–7, 2025 (7 days of data)
- **Granularity**: every 5 minutes, 3 servers → 288 readings/day/server

